[I] Displays many system related stats

[T] Xosview displays many system related stats such as cpu
[T] usage, memory usage, swap usage, network usage,
[T] interrupt activity, serial activity, and load
[T] average inside of an X Window.

[U] https://sourceforge.net/projects/xosview/

[A] Mike Romberg <mike.romberg@noaa.gov>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS NO-LTO.gcc

[L] GPL
[V] 2.3.5

[D] 1d509aa09c47872874bec7a252f9abee8841c4bfdcb35a7ba072e58c xosview2-2.3.5.tar.gz https://download.sourceforge.net/project/xosview/

var_append makeinstopt ' ' 'PREFIX=$root/$prefix' # no DESTDIR
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' "-L`pkgprefix libdir libx11`"
hook_add premake 9 'sed -i -e "s,\$(PREFIX_TO_USE)/lib/X11/app-defaults,$root/`pkgprefix libdir libx11`/X11/app-defaults,g" Makefile'
